Jason,

I used black POR15 during my restoration, and the doors are absolutely
sealed and waterproof. Any other sealer should be carefully checked for
proper adhesion to the inner door surface. POR is really good for this
purpose - Ronnie sells it, as does POR-15 company.

cal


